<h2 style="font-size:1.55rem;margin-bottom:8px;border:none;padding:0;color:var(--ink)">Leading Through Diplomacy: The Consensus Framework</h2>
<p style="color:var(--mid);font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:0;line-height:1.7">Coordinating twelve sovereign academic units – each with its own dean, gift officers, donor strategy, and institutional culture – requires a fundamentally different leadership paradigm than a single chain-of-command organisation. UD&amp;AS operates as a <em>service partner, not a central authority.</em> The credibility to convene, align, and advance a unified philanthropic strategy was built over years through three interlocking principles.</p>
